lemma (in Group) ZassenhausTr2_2:"\<lbrakk>G \<guillemotright> H; G \<guillemotright> H1; G \<guillemotright> K; G \<guillemotright> K1; Gp G H \<triangleright> H1; Gp G K \<triangleright> K1\<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> H1 \<diamondop>\<^bsub>G\<^esub> (H \<inter> K1) \<subseteq> H1 \<diamondop>\<^bsub>G\<^esub> (H \<inter> K)"
